title: Let it All Out ( Latto Interview)
itunes:title: Let it All Out ( Latto Interview)
description:
Today on the show we had Big Latto stop by for the very first time, where she spoke about her first upcoming album "777", BDE Remix, learning the music industry, relationships and more. During the show, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a Brazilian singer hospitalized from holding in her farts around her partner, when in all reality you should just let it out sense farting is the only gas we can afford nowadays! Also, Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"
